story.title: Knows
story.content: A Pisces knows everything and the moment they meet you they can read you like a book.

story.title: Needs
story.content: Romance, Music, Understanding.

story.title: Bad Habit
story.content: Forgiving people that don't deserve your forgiveness.

story.title: Humour
story.content: A Pisces sense of humour is delightfully silly and a bit odd in a good way.

story.title: Strength
story.content: Compassionate, Artistic, Intuitive, Gentle, Wise, Musical.

story.title: Weakness
story.content: Fearful, Overly trusting, sad, Desire to escape reality, Can be a victim or a martyr.

story.title: Likes
story.content: Being alone, Sleeping, Music, Romance, Visual media, Swimming, Spiritual themes.

story.title: Dislikes
story.content: Know-it-all, Being criticized, The past coming back to haunt, Cruelty of any kind.

story.title: Mission
story.content: To feel you belong to the soul of the universe. To swim in a current of infinite understanding.

story.title: Have
story.content: You have buckets of compassion and oceans of understanding.

story.title: Story
story.content: You love to immerse yourself in a good story and are good at creating your own stories too.

story.title: Friend
story.content: Gentle and caring, Pisces can be the best friends that may exist.

story.title: Intuitive
story.content: Deeply intuitive, Pisces can sense if something is wrong, even before it happens.

story.title: Expressive
story.content: Pisces are expressive and they will not hesitate to express their feelings to the people around them.

story.title: Compatibility
story.content: Cancer, Scorpio.

story.title: Romantic
story.content: Deep in their hearts, Pisces-born are incorrigible romantics.

story.title: Compatibility
story.content: Virgo

story.title: Learn
story.content: To believe in yourself.

story.title: Create
story.content: As your imagination inspires you, create, create, create.

story.title: Channel
story.content: When you’re distracted or daydreaming, channel this into new projects.

story.title: Don't
story.content: Don't escape into drugs or alcohol—spiral up, not down.
